item.title: Jenny add a quote by George Orwell
item.description: "All political thinking for years past has been vitiated in the same way. People can foresee the future only when it coincides with their own wishes, and the most grossly obvious facts can be ignored when they are unwelcome." -- George Orwell

item.title: Jenny add a quote by George Orwell

item.title: Jenny add a quote by Stephen Roberts
item.description: "I contend that we are both atheists. I just believe in one fewer god than you do. When you understand why you dismiss all the other possible gods, you will understand why I dismiss yours." -- Stephen Roberts
